      <Meanings>
        <Meaning id="12ec8b5e-134f-4745-b5ce-6b7dc086de3f" type="Noun">
          <Vi>Từ điển đồng nghĩa (và đôi khi trái nghĩa)</Vi>
          <En>A reference book or online resource listing words with their synonyms and sometimes antonyms, used to find alternative words with similar meanings.</En>
          <Example>She consulted the thesaurus to find a more precise synonym for "happy."</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="8764a6b3-9b78-41e4-a013-82d34b7c8f5f">
              <Vi>Viết bài, soạn giáo án, hoặc học từ vựng để tránh lặp từ.</Vi>
              <En>Writing an essay, preparing lesson materials, or studying vocabulary to avoid repetition.</En>
            </Situation>
            <Situation id="b51a9805-48eb-4c1f-bb4c-679d57c246d2">
              <Vi>Tra cứu từ đồng nghĩa khi muốn diễn đạt ý tưởng một cách phong phú hơn.</Vi>
              <En>Looking up synonyms when wanting to express an idea more vividly or variably.</En>
            </Situation>
          </Situations>
        </Meaning>
